item.title: Just wow
item.dc:creator: @Pure_Slay Pure Slay
item.description:
@Pure_Slay wrote:

[quote=“Taharok, post:33, topic:415022”][quote author=the elve age link=topic=516980.msg3762537#msg3762537 date=1316981051]

I think they should keep it red.

Yeah but it’s random, they went from 317 to 377 to 474 to 508 etc…

I find it’s quite random about making it 666 o.o

x.x

So I guess you know nothing about 320, 369, 480s, 503, 505, etc? Just because we pick and choose versions doesn’t mean they do, lol. There are reasons the next version will go from 666 to 667.
[/quote]its bigger updates that skip versions correct? Such as 377-400 construction update

That I’m not sure on. 377-400 is the only “jump” I know of, and I don’t even know if it was much of a jump. I’m pretty sure I had my hands on like a 398 client or something at one time, but I am probably wrong. I know almost for a fact that version 400 did exist, so it’s not like there was a jump from 377-420 like many people think. I’m only presuming the reverse is true, additionally, meaning there was no jump at all.[/quote]

After constructions launch, there was probably so many bug patches that caused it to appear to jump so much.

It doesn’t randomly update, they update every week. When it goes from 660-661, then 662 later that day. That means they did bug fixing.

I only update deobs when I need to find new information:
